# Component Library - CGM Dashboard Design System
# Version: 1.0.0
# Created: 2026-05-07
# Source of truth for design tokens and component primitives

## Design System Tokens

### Color Palette

#### Primary
- primary: #4fd1c5
- primary-dark: #38b2ac
- primary-hover: #45b8ad
- primary-active: #3a9d94
- primary-disabled: #a8d5d0

#### Success
- success: #48bb78
- success-dark: #2f855a
- success-light: #c6f6d5
- success-hover: #38a169
- success-active: #2f855a
- success-disabled: #9ae6b4

#### Warning
- warning: #f59e0b
- warning-light: #fefcbf
- warning-hover: #d97706
- warning-active: #b45309
- warning-disabled: #fcd34d

#### Error
- error: #e53e3e
- error-dark: #c53030
- error-light: #fed7d7
- error-hover: #d53f3f
- error-active: #c53030
- error-disabled: #fc8181

#### Info
- info: #2b6cb0
- info-light: #bee3f8
- info-hover: #2563eb
- info-active: #1d4ed8
- info-disabled: #93c5fd

### Background Colors

#### Light Mode
- bg-page: #f8f9fa
- bg-card: #ffffff
- bg-sidebar: #ffffff

#### Dark Mode
- bg-page: #1a202c
- bg-card: #2d3748
- bg-sidebar: #2d3748

### Text Colors

#### Light Mode
- text-primary: #2d3748
- text-secondary: #a0aec0
- text-muted: #718096
- text-medium: #4a5568

#### Dark Mode
- text-primary: #e2e8f0
- text-secondary: #a0aec0
- text-muted: #a0aec0
- text-medium: #cbd5e0

### Spacing Scale

- space-1: 0.25rem (4px)
- space-2: 0.5rem (8px)
- space-3: 0.75rem (12px)
- space-4: 1rem (16px)
- space-5: 1.5rem (24px)
- space-6: 2rem (32px)
- space-8: 3rem (48px)
- space-10: 4rem (64px)
- space-12: 6rem (96px)

### Semantic Spacing

- spacing-xs: space-1 (4px)
- spacing-sm: space-2 (8px)
- spacing-md: space-4 (16px)
- spacing-lg: space-6 (32px)
- spacing-xl: space-8 (48px)

### Border Radius

- radius-sm: 6px
- radius-md: 8px
- radius-lg: 12px
- radius-xl: 15px

### Shadows

- shadow-sm: 0 3.5px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02)
- shadow-card: 0 3.5px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03)

## Component Primitives

### Button (Phase 17)
Variants: primary, secondary, ghost, destructive
Sizes: sm, md, lg
States: default, hover, active, disabled, loading

### Input (Phase 17)
Types: text, number, select, textarea
States: default, focus, error, disabled
Includes: label, helper text, error message

### Card (Phase 17)
Compound: Card.Header, Card.Content, Card.Footer
Variants: default, elevated

### Badge (Phase 17)
Refactored from: StatusBadge
Variants: status colors
Sizes: sm, md

### Theme Toggle (Phase 17)
Options: light, dark, system
Persists: localStorage

## Page References

This library is the source of truth. Page .pen files reference these tokens:
- order-dashboard.pen
- page-layout.pen
- mill-production.pen
- customers.pen
- customer-detail.pen

## Sync Process

1. Design changes start in this file
2. Update src/app/globals.css to match
3. Update .planning/docs/design-tokens.md
4. Run ESLint to verify token usage

